| 7:00-8:00 | Add onboarding | 30-sec time-to-value |
| 8:00-8:30 | Integrate Superwall | Payment flow |
| 8:30-9:00 | Test & polish | Bug-free build |
| 9:00+ | Submit to App Store | SHIPPED |

